I went to Cuba.

00:28:15.600 --> 00:28:15.929
I could see Cuba in fast-forward motion, like a time-lapse.

00:28:15.929 --> 00:28:29.920
All of a sudden, Cuba started growing with economic developments all on the northern side of the island facing towards America.

00:28:54.733 --> 00:28:55.160
It was growing with hotels and industry, and tourist cruise ships were going there.

00:28:55.160 --> 00:29:19.063
Major holiday spots—like people always say, 'Brandon, I want to go there for holiday; I want to go there for a vacation'—it looked like some kind of five-star resorts where you would be waited on hand and foot.

00:29:19.063 --> 00:29:24.651
It was just a blessing of relaxation.

00:29:24.651 --> 00:29:40.640
It looked like some kind of really classy five-star resorts all coming up on the shoreline.

00:30:00.013 --> 00:30:00.547
And I could see the auto industry, but it looked like something like Hawaii, like the economic development in Honolulu.

00:30:00.547 --> 00:30:03.600
That's all I can say.

00:30:06.862 --> 00:30:14.420
I could see men with nice linen shirts and nice hats, smoking cigars, playing golf, and relaxing as if they were on vacation.

00:30:14.420 --> 00:30:17.025
They were drinking special alcohol.

00:30:21.520 --> 00:30:23.680
It looked like a resort.

00:30:23.680 --> 00:30:36.800
As I was looking into it, I could see a great revival coming—all kinds of things when I was looking into Cuba last night.

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:47.880
It looked like a blessing for the Cuban people.

00:30:47.880 --> 00:30:56.053
Then I was praying into California, and the Lord said, 'Do you see?

00:30:56.053 --> 00:31:08.987
' When I paused there, I could see California and I could see the people of California were fed up with Gavin, were fed up with the way their politics are going.

00:31:08.987 --> 00:31:19.404
As we uncover all this great fraud, I saw the people of California becoming outraged, saying 'enough is enough.

00:31:19.404 --> 00:31:41.547
' And the Lord said, 'Pray into this: a red wave of political shaking that would shake the United States and the world for a red wave that would try to come over California, flipping the governor to a Republican, flipping seats into the Republican House.

00:31:41.547 --> 00:31:42.933
' Like Nancy Pelosi, bye-bye.

00:31:42.933 --> 00:31:47.980
A new wave of red trying to spring forth out of California.

00:31:47.980 --> 00:31:57.075
Now, I'm not saying all of it, but I saw red like it was painted red across California.

00:32:04.956 --> 00:32:05.240
And the Lord said, 'Pray into that.

00:32:05.240 --> 00:32:20.020
' There's much more corruption that needs to be uncovered concerning this to bring the people into enlightenment and being enraged that they've been played.

00:32:29.013 --> 00:32:29.227
But the Lord said it's the same over Minnesota.

00:32:29.227 --> 00:32:35.194
Pray for a red wave over Minnesota, for a rising up of people who are fed up.

00:32:50.272 --> 00:32:50.704
I can still see going into November; I was praying into the election.

00:32:50.704 --> 00:32:55.067
The Lord said, 'You can win the Senate.

00:32:55.067 --> 00:32:57.893
' I saw it won by one.

00:33:04.968 --> 00:33:05.252
I was praying to keep it Republican by praying in the right leaders, and I saw one seat.

00:33:05.252 --> 00:33:12.560
Then I saw the House, and the Lord said, 'You can pray this,' and I saw the House staying by more than 20 seats.

00:33:29.290 --> 00:33:29.460
I saw the number 20.

00:33:29.460 --> 00:33:30.033
Remember 20?

00:33:30.733 --> 00:33:31.907
What was that about again?

00:33:33.320 --> 00:33:33.531
I saw 20.

00:33:33.531 --> 00:33:34.800
Was that something personal?

00:33:34.800 --> 00:33:36.480
Yes, it was.

00:33:36.480 --> 00:33:39.968
I've seen so much lately; that was something else.

00:33:39.968 --> 00:33:40.704
So, forgive me.

00:33:40.704 --> 00:33:50.312
I bring personal things in, but it all has to do with the same thing, doesn't it?

00:33:50.312 --> 00:33:52.520
Praying into the 20.

00:34:07.260 --> 00:34:13.160
I keep praying into these things that the Lord is talking to me about—my personal ministry, the time frames of things, and praying for President Trump because he said he's tired.

00:34:13.160 --> 00:34:14.759
He needs help.

00:34:23.679 --> 00:34:29.399
And that's why I tried to tell you all—I wasn't trying to pick at him last night, but I'm going to tell you, you must pray for him.

00:34:29.399 --> 00:34:32.494
He won't make it without our prayers.

00:34:32.494 --> 00:34:44.145
It gets to the point where you all need to have discernment for yourselves.

00:34:57.488 --> 00:34:58.184
You need to hear God for yourself, but you need to filter it with the Word.

00:34:58.184 --> 00:35:03.325
Everything you are hearing and how you try to correct me—filter it with the Scripture.

00:35:03.325 --> 00:35:05.275
Pray about our nation.

00:35:05.275 --> 00:35:09.008
Pray for us to be a sheep nation.

00:35:18.015 --> 00:35:18.240
Pray for us to stay and have a great revival.

00:35:18.240 --> 00:35:22.944
Pray for a shaking and awakening in the churches.

00:35:22.944 --> 00:35:35.029
But when you're praying and seeing into things, like I said, we see in part and hear in part.

00:35:35.029 --> 00:35:41.293
You think things are right here—it looks like it's right on your nose—but yet it's just a couple years out.

00:35:45.733 --> 00:35:45.987
It could be a little further out than what you think.

00:35:45.987 --> 00:35:53.470
Because in our natural mind, we don't understand the spirit realm when it comes to time.

00:35:53.470 --> 00:35:53.980
God's vast.

00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:09.140
There is no beginning and there is no end.

00:36:09.140 --> 00:36:15.075
So His timing of when He says something's coming—and you say, 'Soon, Brandon, when is soon?

00:36:15.075 --> 00:36:23.385
'—soon to God could be 10 years, 20 years, or a lot of things.

00:36:26.560 --> 00:36:30.893
But you don't try to add to or take away from anything you hear or see.

00:36:33.320 --> 00:36:35.013
I deliver it as I see it.

00:36:36.860 --> 00:36:39.204
To add a time frame to it would be really stupid.

00:36:52.223 --> 00:36:52.377
To say, 'Well, this is my opinion'—who cares about Brandon Biggs's opinion?

00:36:52.377 --> 00:36:55.329
I'm just as flawed as you all are.

00:36:55.329 --> 00:36:55.987
Everybody has issues.

00:36:59.760 --> 00:37:00.208
I don't exalt myself above anything.

00:37:00.208 --> 00:37:02.000
That's what I'm telling you all.

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:02.782
I'm just human.

00:37:02.978 --> 00:37:05.653
I have issues I'm overcoming just like you all do.

00:37:05.653 --> 00:37:09.240
I'm just a person used just like you all are.

00:37:09.240 --> 00:37:13.183
Regardless, this channel and everything has just been God's grace.

00:37:16.360 --> 00:37:16.560
Everybody has something we're working through.

00:37:16.560 --> 00:37:21.103
Everyone has something that you're seeking Him for—healing, finances, protection, whatever it may be.

00:37:23.237 --> 00:37:28.040
But we work out our salvation with fear and trembling.

00:37:29.055 --> 00:37:32.707
That's what I try to tell you all: when you get real with God, God will become real to you.

00:37:39.040 --> 00:37:39.320
I get tired of all the celebrity charismatic Christian stuff; it is over the top.

00:37:40.160 --> 00:37:47.080
When you talk to people and they're real with you, they are just as real.

00:37:47.080 --> 00:37:50.040
They go through things just like you do.

00:37:50.040 --> 00:37:51.853
We're all a work in progress.

00:37:51.853 --> 00:37:55.453
Humble yourselves underneath the mighty hand of God.

00:37:55.453 --> 00:37:56.213
Humble yourself.

00:37:56.213 --> 00:37:58.366
That's the bottom line.

00:37:58.366 --> 00:38:02.407
There is so much spiritual pride, and I see it all the time.

00:38:03.105 --> 00:38:06.347
A lot of arrogant people, and you go, 'Hold on a minute.

00:38:12.834 --> 00:38:15.680
Don't you realize that I walk in a seer's anointing, and I can see all your mess, and I never tell anyone anything?

00:38:24.040 --> 00:38:24.310
I see the mess on a lot of people that think they have a lot going on for them.

00:38:24.310 --> 00:38:36.600
Some of them are on TV, and I look at them and go, 'But the Lord reveals everything about your business to tell me to pray for you.

00:38:36.600 --> 00:38:40.512
' He says, 'Listen, don't be like that.

00:38:40.512 --> 00:38:42.470
Humble yourself, Brandon.

00:38:42.470 --> 00:38:43.570
Remember the janitor.

00:38:43.570 --> 00:38:51.053
' It's interesting as a watchman because I see things that nobody else will see because the Lord allows me to.

00:38:51.053 --> 00:39:00.326
Then he shows me things about myself all the time, and I don't even feel worthy to do anything.

00:39:00.326 --> 00:39:24.960
Some days I say, 'God, thank God it's all by your grace,' but it really sets the stage for me to realize it has nothing to do with you and everything to do with how good God is and how merciful he is that he would even look in my direction.

00:39:24.960 --> 00:39:27.325
It's all by his grace.

00:39:39.855 --> 00:39:43.880
I said, 'God, thank you for using somebody like me.

00:39:43.880 --> 00:39:51.330
' The other night—I try to explain this all the time—I don't know if he's going to show up tonight.

00:39:51.330 --> 00:39:53.613
I don't control it.

00:39:53.613 --> 00:40:02.020
Sometimes people want you to snap your fingers and think you control it and make this happen.

00:40:10.760 --> 00:40:11.120
But I can't control any of it.

00:40:11.120 --> 00:40:13.640
I am yielded to him.

00:40:13.640 --> 00:40:14.973
I'm just here.

00:40:14.973 --> 00:40:20.307
If you choose to use me again, fine.

00:40:20.307 --> 00:40:29.005
But I don't know how long I'll be doing this because I don't control any of it.

00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:35.680
He could say, 'I'm done tomorrow,' and I'll be there saying, 'Well, okay.

00:40:35.680 --> 00:40:43.550
I'll go back to selling on eBay and Poshmark full-time, really hitting it hard, trying to find things to flip.

00:40:43.550 --> 00:40:49.547
' Diana does it now, but I used to help her with the measurements.

00:40:49.547 --> 00:40:56.320
I'd sit there for hours and measure all the clothes for the people because they always want to return them.

00:40:56.320 --> 00:41:04.980
eBay's return policy is terrible; you have to measure all the armpits and tell everybody if there's a stain.

00:41:04.980 --> 00:41:06.720
That was my job.

00:41:06.720 --> 00:41:11.542
Now Diana does that by herself, bless her heart.

00:41:12.084 --> 00:41:13.615
But it is what it is.

00:41:22.280 --> 00:41:31.504
I just want to tell you, that's why I try to say I'll pastor and I'll teach you all prayer and do what God's called me to do until he tells me to do something else.

00:41:31.504 --> 00:41:37.418
Whenever he told me about praying and having a theater in Branson, I didn't know when I would do it.

00:41:37.884 --> 00:41:39.704
I priced them; they're high dollar, millions of dollars.

00:41:39.704 --> 00:41:42.280
So you go, 'Okay, what does ministry look like?

00:41:42.280 --> 00:41:45.640
' I always say, 'What's your five-year plan?

00:41:45.640 --> 00:41:48.060
What's your 10-year goal?

00:41:48.060 --> 00:41:55.780
' If the Lord carries, where will I be by the time I'm such and such age, 50 or 60 years old, whatever?

00:41:59.712 --> 00:42:00.008
What do you want to do?

00:42:00.008 --> 00:42:09.484
Because I had a dream to get here to pray and do what God's called me to do, but it took years.

00:42:09.484 --> 00:42:26.313
As I was praying this morning, he said, 'You don't realize all the years that you were on the back side of the desert as a janitor at that church, being a janitor at that mega-ministry, being a janitor here and doing what I've called you to do.

00:42:27.400 --> 00:42:30.812
I was growing great taproots with you.

00:42:30.812 --> 00:42:33.740
' I said, 'What do you mean?

00:42:33.740 --> 00:42:47.730
' He said, 'You're freaking out because of all the fruit and all that I've done and how everything has happened so quickly, but it took years of cultivation that nobody saw.

00:42:47.730 --> 00:42:51.760
There were great roots that I've had growing way down deep.

00:43:10.000 --> 00:43:10.920
The greater the root, the greater the growth of the tree can be to sustain it because a strong wind can't blow over a tree that has great roots.

00:43:10.920 --> 00:43:18.840
' And he said just because you didn't see the outward growth doesn't mean I wasn't growing a deep taproot with you, Brandon and Diana.

00:43:18.840 --> 00:43:24.645
He said, 'Don't underestimate the 20-some years I had you being a janitor and doing what you did.

00:43:24.645 --> 00:43:29.987
There were great taproots as you said yes to everything I told you to do.

00:43:29.987 --> 00:43:46.960
' So I say to you, you may not see much fruit on the outside right now, but God has cultivated great taproots on the inside of you that have gone way down deep in the Holy Ghost soil, the soil of life.

00:43:48.320 --> 00:43:51.260
And you think, 'When is my time?

00:43:51.260 --> 00:43:54.060
When is God going to do this?

00:43:54.060 --> 00:44:00.870
When is he going to bring the promises of the prophecies spoken over my life?

00:44:00.880 --> 00:44:07.200
' He told me I was going to do this.

00:44:07.200 --> 00:44:11.613
I'm the coat of many colors, but yet I'm in the prison.

00:44:11.613 --> 00:44:14.010
That's what you may feel.

00:44:14.760 --> 00:44:30.371
I have a prophecy, a coat of many colors, and yet my brother sold me into slavery.

00:44:39.600 --> 00:44:39.880
And now I'm in Potiphar's house, and the blessing's on it and it's prospering, but his wife accused me of this and now I'm in prison.

00:44:39.880 --> 00:44:41.800
How many years go by?

00:44:44.160 --> 00:44:57.124
But the taproot was growing so deep in the soil that when Joseph got to the place of his time—it's time for you, buddy, to be second-in-command of all of Egypt—the fruit that was displayed came because the root went much deeper.

00:45:01.480 --> 00:45:01.710
Does that make sense?

00:45:07.680 --> 00:45:07.900
The character that it took to handle it so he wouldn't become arrogant.

00:45:07.900 --> 00:45:11.360
They would say, 'Look at you now.

00:45:11.360 --> 00:45:17.080
You were broken and you were humbled.

00:45:17.080 --> 00:45:32.800
' That's why I realize whenever the Lord speaks to me about some of these things he's told me to do, I keep that janitor in and I don't want to deviate from it.

00:45:32.800 --> 00:45:44.291
So help me because, honestly, the more this keeps growing, and I know I live in a Christian state...

00:45:44.291 --> 00:45:50.840
maybe it wouldn't be so bad in California; people might not notice me as much.

00:45:51.370 --> 00:45:55.280
But the more this happens, the more I grow.

00:45:55.280 --> 00:46:02.733
When you live in an area where there's a lot of believers, I'm not into the celebrity stuff.

00:46:02.733 --> 00:46:05.100
I just don't care about it.

00:46:17.049 --> 00:46:17.391
To me, this is like whatever.

00:46:17.391 --> 00:46:23.067
It's just growing pains, just learning how to deal with all this.

00:46:23.067 --> 00:46:32.070
This is a learning process for me.

00:46:32.080 --> 00:46:33.270
I'm just real with you.

00:46:33.270 --> 00:46:48.006
That's why I tell you when I come in here, I don't know if he's going to show up.

00:46:48.006 --> 00:46:49.080
I just trust.

00:46:49.080 --> 00:46:51.320
He says, 'Do it.

00:46:51.320 --> 00:46:54.520
' Okay, I'll do it.

00:46:54.520 --> 00:46:58.440
'You want me to pray with the people tonight?

00:46:58.440 --> 00:46:59.340
' Yeah.

00:46:59.340 --> 00:47:02.503
'What do you want me to say?

00:47:02.503 --> 00:47:04.587
' What you're saying.

00:47:04.587 --> 00:47:05.880
Certain things.

00:47:05.880 --> 00:47:09.720
He'll tell me to shut up like earlier.

00:47:09.720 --> 00:47:20.507
It's interesting because there's a lot of you that are believing for your manifestation of what you're believing for.

00:47:20.507 --> 00:47:27.896
I'm just telling you, Brandon Biggs, just try to be obedient.

00:47:27.896 --> 00:47:32.775
Whatever he's told me to do, I've done it.

00:47:32.775 --> 00:47:38.780
He said, 'Fill up the water pots like he did at the wedding supper.

00:47:38.780 --> 00:47:48.390
' And he said, 'It's not my time yet, woman.

00:47:48.390 --> 00:48:01.526
' Then he went up there and filled up the water pots and boom, the water turned into wine.

00:48:01.526 --> 00:48:05.943
Whatever he tells you to do, do it.

00:48:06.833 --> 00:48:08.727
I just do it.

00:48:08.727 --> 00:48:14.340
He said, 'I didn't call you to be in front of a pulpit yet.

00:48:14.340 --> 00:48:16.140
That day is coming.

00:48:20.330 --> 00:48:20.540
You go in front of a camera.

00:48:20.540 --> 00:48:21.969
' Hopefully that helps somebody.

00:48:32.514 --> 00:48:32.851
I know that's a lot of something, but I tried to tell you the process because this is all so interesting to me.

00:48:32.851 --> 00:48:46.657
Over the last three years—it'll be three years in June—of just growing, and now we reach millions and millions of people for Jesus every month.

00:48:46.657 --> 00:48:47.909
Millions, literally.

00:48:47.909 --> 00:48:49.985
All glory to God.

00:48:49.985 --> 00:48:57.067
Then Facebook contacted us today and said, 'We want to discuss things with you over the phone.

00:48:57.067 --> 00:49:02.210
' I said, 'I don't want to talk to you.

00:49:02.210 --> 00:49:23.556
' It was funny because they banned me, and then one of their big people reached out to us and said, 'We want to talk to you over the phone about some of the things you're posting and if you want to be reinstated back on our platform.

00:49:23.556 --> 00:49:35.960
' I think the whole thing is interesting because I was just like, 'What do they want to say to us over the phone?

00:49:35.960 --> 00:49:41.702
' But we'll talk to them and we'll go back on Facebook.

00:49:41.702 --> 00:49:44.880
Maybe I'll not compromise what God has told me to say.

00:49:44.880 --> 00:49:58.429
He said, 'I want you to say the hard things,' and I'll continue to do it and I'm sold out to it.

00:49:58.429 --> 00:50:03.697
It's not always going to be easy.

00:50:03.697 --> 00:50:08.432
He said, 'Brandon, I didn't tell you it would be easy.

00:50:13.017 --> 00:50:13.440
I said I'd be with you and it's doable.

00:50:13.440 --> 00:50:19.520
' I said, 'What am I supposed to say to that?

00:50:25.000 --> 00:50:25.349
I never told you it'd be easy.

00:50:25.349 --> 00:50:32.344
' Diana, we laugh about that all the time when Jesus said that.

00:50:32.344 --> 00:50:36.905
He said, 'I never told you it'd be easy.

00:50:36.905 --> 00:50:39.490
' Brandon, you have anything?

00:50:39.490 --> 00:50:42.480
I've talked way too long.

00:50:42.480 --> 00:50:43.500
Right.

00:50:43.500 --> 00:50:44.100
Yeah.

00:50:44.100 --> 00:50:46.190
What building is that, baby?

00:50:48.360 --> 00:50:49.560
I was trying to find that beat.

00:50:49.560 --> 00:50:51.905
No one sent a beat.

00:51:10.760 --> 00:51:11.080
It doesn't work.

00:51:11.080 --> 00:51:17.090
Don't worry about it.

00:51:17.090 --> 00:51:19.418
We're way past that now.

00:51:19.418 --> 00:51:19.889
Okay.

00:51:23.960 --> 00:51:29.400
So, we're going to pray over President Trump and the decision he's going to make by tomorrow.

00:51:29.400 --> 00:51:41.657
As I've rambled, I want you to hear what he said concerning this video about the spies.

00:51:41.657 --> 00:51:46.160
Do you remember when I told you we had rats?

00:51:46.160 --> 00:51:49.680
We have rats in the Pentagon.

00:51:49.680 --> 00:51:53.520
Does anybody remember?

00:52:04.160 --> 00:52:04.707
I want you just to be real.

00:52:04.707 --> 00:52:22.423
Do you remember when I told you there were rats in the Pentagon and I told you he had badges all over his vest?

00:52:39.171 --> 00:52:39.594
And I saw him.

00:52:46.000 --> 00:52:46.230
I saw a man and I said, 'Watch.

00:52:46.230 --> 00:52:49.297
There's rats in the Pentagon and he's leaking information.

00:52:49.297 --> 00:52:51.743
' Look at this.

00:52:54.347 --> 00:52:54.740
This is very interesting today.

00:52:54.740 --> 00:53:01.000
Does anybody remember me saying there were rats in the Pentagon?

00:53:01.000 --> 00:53:03.010
There's rats in the White House.

00:53:03.010 --> 00:53:04.229
There's rats.

00:53:04.229 --> 00:53:07.420
They're around President Trump.

00:53:14.320 --> 00:53:14.713
Now, listen to this.

00:53:30.520 --> 00:53:30.800
This is interesting when you add that to it.

00:53:30.800 --> 00:53:41.286
We have to find that leaker because that's a sick person.

00:53:41.286 --> 00:53:51.640
They probably didn't realize the extent of how bad it was.

00:54:07.031 --> 00:54:07.249
I can't imagine that the person did, but we're going to find out.

00:54:14.897 --> 00:54:17.140
It's national security, and the person that did the story will go to jail if he doesn't say.

00:54:18.920 --> 00:54:19.640
And that doesn't last long.

00:54:34.080 --> 00:54:34.420
I think everybody would understand it.

00:54:49.105 --> 00:54:49.430
They put this mission at great risk.

00:55:05.430 --> 00:55:05.700
They put that man at great risk and they put the hundreds of people that went in looking for him because everyone now knows that we're going in.

00:55:05.700 --> 00:55:07.848
Don't you think that's interesting?

00:55:07.848 --> 00:55:13.634
We have to figure out who the leaker is.

00:55:13.634 --> 00:55:14.834
Who's the leaker?

00:55:14.834 --> 00:55:16.480
Who's telling our secrets?

00:55:16.480 --> 00:55:22.189
Somebody in the press, but where'd they get it from?

00:55:22.189 --> 00:55:23.973
Who's the leaker?

00:55:23.973 --> 00:55:25.783
Who's leaking?

00:55:25.783 --> 00:55:29.263
Time is up actually today.

